[eonetdata://<name>]
category = List of all the available event categories in the EONET system.
sources = List of all the available event sources in the EONET system.
status = Events that have ended are assigned a closed date. The existence of that date will allow to filter for only-open or only-closed events. Omitting the status parameter will return currently open events.
days = Limit the number of prior days (including today) from which events will be returned.
limit = Limits the number of events returned.